From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: WebKitGTKWin Port <webkitgtkwin@ooblerg.local>
Date: Wed, 17 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] WebKitGTKWin: stage UnixFileDescriptor for GTK Windows

The GTK accelerated backing IPC messages still mention UnixFileDescriptor
while the Windows port keeps that path compiling out its Unix transport
implementation. Stage the lightweight wrapper header for WIN32 so the
generated receivers and GTK headers can compile while the platform backend
split continues.
---
 Source/WTF/wtf/PlatformGTK.cmake | 2 ++
 1 file changed, 2 insertions(+)

diff --git a/Source/WTF/wtf/PlatformGTK.cmake b/Source/WTF/wtf/PlatformGTK.cmake
index 1a73669..2b77ea7 100644
--- a/Source/WTF/wtf/PlatformGTK.cmake
+++ b/Source/WTF/wtf/PlatformGTK.cmake
@@ -89,6 +89,8 @@ if (WIN32)
         win/SoftLinking.h
         win/WTFCRTDebug.h
         win/Win32Handle.h
+
+        unix/UnixFileDescriptor.h
     )
 else ()
     list(APPEND WTF_PUBLIC_HEADERS
-- 
2.45.0
